steps:['Identify all stakeholders (anyone who affects or is affected by the change)','Rate each stakeholder on: Interest (low-high) and Power/Influence (low-high)','Plot on a Power-Interest grid','Develop engagement strategy for each quadrant: Manage Closely, Keep Satisfied, Keep Informed, Monitor','Implement engagement actions','Monitor stakeholder sentiment throughout'],
