steps:['Collect all complaints through multiple channels (verbal, written, online)','Acknowledge and respond to individual complaints promptly (24–48 hours)','Categorize complaints (communication, waiting, clinical care, environment, staff attitude, billing)','Quantify and trend by category over time','Identify the top 3–5 categories using Pareto Analysis','Investigate root causes of high-frequency categories','Implement improvements','Follow up with complainants','Report to quality committee'],
benefits:['Patient feedback = free quality audit','Identifies patterns missed by clinical monitoring','Improves patient satisfaction','Regulatory requirement'],
